Former head of the Department of Business Administration, Auchi Polytechnic, Dr. Clement Osoba-Enakali, has died. Osoba attended St. Anthony Catholic School, Uromi, where he obtained his First School Leaving CertificateÂ  and Ishan Grammar School. He attended Auchi Polytechnic for his National Diploma and Higher National Diploma before proceeding to the University of Benin for his postgraduate studies. He is survived by his wife Justina and three children. He was buried on July 27.